{"tid":2242884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慘！塔利班表態挺川普遭拒 「破壞和談」被美軍空襲教訓","createTime":"2020-10-14T10:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T11:03:58.000Z","uid":337052,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"86e386c4eae776332f0a6caf66bf063a06285d1d","tid":2242884,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">慘！塔利班表態挺川普遭拒 「破壞和談」被美軍空襲教訓</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/14/phpfHfNwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F14%2FphpfHfNwn.jpg&h=b9deece2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塔利班武裝份子在過去一週於該省不同地區發動攻擊，在週末更加劇攻擊行動，主要高速公路上的橋樑遭炸毀，道路被迫關閉。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n2020/10/14 17:53<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">阿富汗民兵組織塔利班（Taliban）日前公開表態支持川普連任，並關心確診武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）的川普身體是否健康。對此，川普團隊馬上聲明「我們拒絕塔利班的支持」，沒多久後，美國空軍也對阿富汗赫爾曼德省南部的塔利班組織發動空襲。</span><br />\n<br />\n根據美媒11日報導，塔利班發言人穆賈希德（Zabihullah Mujahid）日前受訪時大讚川普，表態希望他能贏得勝選，並讓美軍從阿富汗撤軍。穆賈希德在訪問中，也對先前確診的川普表達關心；對此，<span class=\"red\">川普競選團隊立刻聲明「拒絕塔利班的支持」</span>，聲明並指美國總統會以美國的利益優先。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，美國空軍發言人萊格特上校（Sonny Leggett）12日在推特PO文，<span class=\"red\">證實過去2天在阿富汗赫爾曼德省發動空襲</span>，並引美軍在阿富汗指揮官官米勒將軍（Scott Miller）的話指出，塔利班必須停止在赫爾曼德省的攻擊行動，減少這種與先前協議不符的暴力行為，也破壞了阿富汗內部正在進行的和平談判。<br />\n<br />\n萊格特上校表示，美空軍將持續對阿富汗提供防禦支援，協助抵禦塔利班組織攻擊。根據阿富汗赫爾曼德省發言人茨瓦克（Omer Zwak）表示，塔利班武裝份子在過去一週於該省不同地區發動攻擊，在週末更加劇攻擊行動，主要高速公路上的橋樑遭炸毀，道路被迫關閉。而目前阿富汗政府正與塔利班代表在卡塔爾舉行內部談判，旨在結束阿富汗長年以來的戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USFOR_A/status/1315602844809080832?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1315602844809080832%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3321224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSFOR_A%2Fstatus%2F1315602844809080832%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1315602844809080832%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnews.ltn.com.tw%252Fnews%252Fworld%252Fbreakingnews%252F3321224&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=3afadafa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSFOR_A%2Fstatus%2F1315602844809080832%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1315602844809080832%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnews.ltn.com.tw%252Fnews%252Fworld%252Fbreakingnews%252F3321224&h=1e87cc14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USFOR_A/status/1315602844809080832?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1315602844809080832%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3321224</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3321224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3321224&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2kuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=0e60d95e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3321224&h=8cea0b82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3321224</a>"},{"pid":"618f51f035ff517c3ae5bf28fedcb815e88f69b2","tid":2242884,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:43:09.000Z","msg":"摟打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d422cfbb3f9f0048c81189a0e18f6f4699477ea5","tid":2242884,"uid":47492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"擺明靠害  塔利班收左支那幾多錢"},{"pid":"2fb06ad37e9dd4da870f5c2e1e6f73ed93188f75","tid":2242884,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d422cfbb3f9f0048c81189a0e18f6f4699477ea5","tid":2242884,"uid":47492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"擺明靠害  塔利班收左支那幾多錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:44:06.000Z","msg":